  <entry>
    <title>JoinGiftItem插件</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/posts/c73577a4.html"/>
    <id>http://example.com/posts/c73577a4.html</id>
    <published>2022-07-27T03:43:44.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-12-16T01:43:17.413Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<table><thead><tr><th>插件名称</th><th align="right">语言</th><th align="center">日志</th><th align="left">版本</th><th align="left">最后更新时间</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>JoinGiftItem</td><td align="right">Java</td><td align="center">插件诞生</td><td align="left">1.0V</td><td align="left">2022-7-27</td></tr><tr><td>JoinGiftItem</td><td align="right">Java</td><td align="center">修复bug</td><td align="left">1.0V</td><td align="left">2022-8-2</td></tr><tr><td>JoinGiftItem</td><td align="right">Java</td><td align="center">新增功能</td><td align="left">1.1V</td><td align="left">2022-8-4</td></tr></tbody></table><table><thead><tr><th align="right">是否开源</th><th align="right">开源地址</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="right">是,代码没更新</td><td align="right"><a href="https://github.com/BackRer/QQPlugins">https://github.com/BackRer/QQPlugins</a></td></tr></tbody></table><table><thead><tr><th align="right">下载地址</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="right"><a href="https://github.com/BackRer/QQPlugins/releases/tag/plugins">https://github.com/BackRer/QQPlugins/releases/tag/plugins</a> 更新慢</td></tr><tr><td align="right"><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1AuXWI_ktuYEIKuueT9sfyw">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1AuXWI_ktuYEIKuueT9sfyw</a> 提取码：omva 更新快</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="安装方法"><a href="#安装方法" class="headerlink" title="安装方法"></a>安装方法</h3><p>下载好插件放入&#x2F;plugins内重启服务器即可.</p><hr><h3 id="简介-amp-用法"><a href="#简介-amp-用法" class="headerlink" title="简介&amp;用法"></a>简介&amp;用法</h3><p>JoinGiftItem是一款可以在玩家不在线时给予物品的插件,可以自定义给予礼包。<br>指令:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rqs help</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>玩家指令:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">myjoin help</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可查看全部用法.</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">§6==========§b[§cRconQQShop§b]§6==========</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs getItem §c获取手中物品英文id</span><br><span class="line">§6==========§b[§cItem§b]§6==========</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs help §c查看帮助指令</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs addItem [id] [物品英文id] §c给予一名玩家待领取物品</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs listItem [id] §c列出一名玩家当前待领取物品</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs removeItem [id] [物品英文id] §c删除一名玩家待领取物品</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs clearItem [id] §c删除一名玩家所有待领取物品</span><br><span class="line">§6==========§b[§cGift§b]§6==========</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs gift §c打开现有礼包</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs gift [礼包名称] §c打开指定礼包</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs giftAdd [id] [礼包代码] §c给指定玩家添加一个礼包</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs giftdelete [id] [礼包代码] §c删除一名玩家的特定礼包</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs giftlist [id] §c列出当前玩家的所有礼包</span><br><span class="line">§a/rqs giftclear [id] §c删除当前玩家的所有礼包</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h4 id="实例"><a href="#实例" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rqs addItem BackRer BOW</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>这里物品<code>id</code>一定要用英文的,如果不知道英文id多少可以手持物品输入<code>/rqs getitem</code>来获取英文<code>id</code>.</strong><br><img src="/./img/JoinGiftItem/1.png"><br>这样当玩家上线时就会提醒玩家有一个要领取.</p><hr><h4 id="配置文件"><a href="#配置文件" class="headerlink" title="配置文件"></a>配置文件</h4><p><code>config.yml</code>内包含了汉化信息和标题的配置.(不要问我为什么把汉化也放在config了)</p><hr><h5 id="修改提示信息"><a href="#修改提示信息" class="headerlink" title="修改提示信息"></a>修改提示信息</h5><p>在<code>config.yml</code>中找到<code>JoinMessage</code>进行修改.<br>这里<code>/item_list_size/</code>代表有多少个待领取物品数量，<code>/gift_list_siez</code>代表有多少个待领取礼包数量.</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JoinMessage:</span><br><span class="line">  - &quot;§b----------------------------&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  - &quot;§c您当前有§d /item_list_size/ §c个物品等待你领取！&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  - &quot;§b/gift_list_size/个礼包待你领取！&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  - &quot;§b----------------------------&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h5 id="gift-yml文件配置"><a href="#gift-yml文件配置" class="headerlink" title="gift.yml文件配置"></a>gift.yml文件配置</h5><p><del>在这里我画个大饼,下一个版本或许会支持gui配置。</del></p><h1 id="Gift为头标题请勿修改"><a href="#Gift为头标题请勿修改" class="headerlink" title="Gift为头标题请勿修改."></a><code>Gift</code>为头标题请勿修改.</h1><h1 id="Text为礼包代号用于rqs-giftAdd-id-礼包代码-中的礼包代号-lore为这个礼包的描述信息-Item为这个礼包的所有的物品Item格式"><a href="#Text为礼包代号用于rqs-giftAdd-id-礼包代码-中的礼包代号-lore为这个礼包的描述信息-Item为这个礼包的所有的物品Item格式" class="headerlink" title="Text为礼包代号用于rqs giftAdd [id] [礼包代码] 中的礼包代号.lore为这个礼包的描述信息.Item为这个礼包的所有的物品Item格式"></a><code>Text</code>为礼包代号用于rqs giftAdd [id] [礼包代码] 中的礼包代号.<br><code>lore</code>为这个礼包的描述信息.<br><code>Item</code>为这个礼包的所有的物品<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Gift:</span><br><span class="line">  Text:</span><br><span class="line">    name: Demo</span><br><span class="line">    lore: &amp;id005</span><br><span class="line">    - lore1</span><br><span class="line">    - lore2</span><br><span class="line">    - lore1</span><br><span class="line">    - lore2</span><br><span class="line">    Item:</span><br><span class="line">      Item1:</span><br><span class="line">        mate: BOW</span><br><span class="line">        displayname: This A BOW!</span><br><span class="line">        size: 1</span><br><span class="line">        lore: *id005</span><br><span class="line">      Item2:</span><br><span class="line">        mate: BOW</span><br><span class="line">        displayname: This A BOW Two!</span><br><span class="line">        size: 1</span><br><span class="line">        lore: *id005</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><code>Item</code>格式</h1><p><code>mate</code>为物品英文id<br><code>displayname</code>为物品的显示名称<br><code>size</code>物品数量<br><code>lore</code> 为物品描述,可配置多行</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Item:</span><br><span class="line">  Item1:</span><br><span class="line">    mate: BOW</span><br><span class="line">    displayname: This A BOW!</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1</span><br><span class="line">    lore: []</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="更新"><a href="#更新" class="headerlink" title="更新"></a>更新</h3><h4 id="2022-x2F-8-x2F-4"><a href="#2022-x2F-8-x2F-4" class="headerlink" title="2022&#x2F;8&#x2F;4"></a>2022&#x2F;8&#x2F;4</h4><p>新增指令:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/myjoin bind 查看/创建code码&quot;</span><br><span class="line">/myjoin binds 强制更新自己的code码&quot;</span><br><span class="line">================================</span><br><span class="line">/rqs bind [id] [code] 强制修改一名玩家的code&quot;</span><br><span class="line">/rqs binds [id] 查看一名玩家的code&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
